title: Former Catalan leader Artur Mas on the referendum, independence and plan for talks  - BBC Newsnight
description:
Former Catalan leader Artur Mas speaks to Emily Maitlis as current president Carles Puigdemont says he will deliver the on independence vote - but asks the Catalan parliament to suspend the result to enable talks with Madrid.

Newsnight is the BBC's flagship news and current affairs TV programme - with analysis, debate, exclusives, and robust interviews.
